name: Doppelgator
printed_effect:
Elestrals that are not {lunar}/{solar}-Enchanted get -1 {attack}
for each {lunar} Enchanting this Doppelgator.
When this Dopplegator receives 1 or more
{lunar}/{wind} in a Nexus you can Special Ascend it to
Fulgoryx from your hand or deck.
